headline: MIKE MELIGRIGORIS RECOGNIZED BY BENEFITS AND PENSIONS MONITOR
summary: T. Rowe Price (Canada), Inc., is pleased to announce Mike Meligrigoris' inclusion in Benefits and Pensions Monitor's(BPM) third annual "Hot List", recognizing financial professionals who are helping to shape the future of Canada's benefits, pension, and institutional investment sectors.

headline: 3 Financials Stocks That Fall Short
summary: Financial providers use their expertise in capital allocation and risk assessment to help facilitate economic growth while offering consumers and businesses essential financial services. But uncertainty about fiscal and monetary policy has tempered enthusiasm, limiting the industry's gains to 20.7% over the past six months. This return lagged the S&P 500's 24.7% climb.
